descriptionHtml:
This mod retextures Whiterun with a texture pack inspired by Bruma from TES IV: Oblivion. It also affects the appearance of any other in game assets that use the same textures. The alternate version changes the roofs to black dragontile instead of thatched. 

Also changes some buildings in dlcs (Hearthfire houses, Skaal village) but, none are required to use my mod. 

[b]-Compatibility-[/b] 

The two versions are not compatible with each other, so only download either the alternate or original version. 

Also not compatible with other Whiterun retextures

[b]-Installation- 
[/b]
Paste the file into the Skyrim/Data folder.

[b]-Uninstallation-[/b]

Delete this file:Skyrim\Data\textures\architecture\whiterun
author: Jangosan
